  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Bamboo</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p><i>Exclusive to:</i> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shipwrecked\" title=\"Shipwrecked\"><img alt=\"Shipwrecked icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Shipwrecked_icon.png/32px-Shipwrecked_icon.png?3f6ffb\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet\" title=\"Hamlet\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/32px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p><b>Bamboo</b> is a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Renewable_resources\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Renewable resources\">renewable</a> resource that can be gathered by hacking down a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Bamboo_Patch\" title=\"Bamboo Patch\">Bamboo Patch</a> with a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Machete\" title=\"Machete\">Machete</a> in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Shipwrecked\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Shipwrecked\">Shipwrecked</a></i> DLC. It can also be obtained by hammering a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wildbore_House\" title=\"Wildbore House\">Wildbore House</a> or a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wildbore_Head\" title=\"Wildbore Head\">Wildbore Head</a>.\n</p><p>It is used in many <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nautical\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Nautical\">Nautical</a> recipes and can also be refined into <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cloth\" title=\"Cloth\">Cloth</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Hamlet\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Hamlet_icon\" title=\"Hamlet icon\"><img alt=\"Hamlet icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Hamlet_icon.png/32px-Hamlet_icon.png?e04a83\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a> Hamlet</span></h2>\n<p>Bamboo is also included in the <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve:_Hamlet\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve: Hamlet\">Hamlet</a></i> DLC where it can be bought for 3 <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Oinc\" title=\"Oinc\">Oincs</a> at <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/%27The_Sty%27_Oddities_Emporium\" title=\"&#x27;The Sty&#x27; Oddities Emporium\">&#x27;The Sty&#x27; Oddities Emporium</a> in the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pig_City\" title=\"Pig City\">Pig City</a>. There is also a small chance(around 7%) for Bamboo to be obtained from hammering the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/A_Smashing_Pot\" title=\"A Smashing Pot\">&#x27;A Smashing Pot</a>. Using a <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shears\" title=\"Shears\">Shears</a> on a Bamboo Patch will result in 2 <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Bamboo</a> instead of the usual one. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Placeholder\" title=\"Placeholder\"><img alt=\"Placeholder.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Placeholder.png/32px-Placeholder.png?210282\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\"></a> Trivia</span></h2>\n<ul><li>It was originally assumed that Bamboo was a Wood Food Type and could also be eaten by Werebeaver and would give 10 Beaverness</li></ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
