  "schema_version": 1,
  "summaryViHtml": "<h2>Tóm tắt</h2><p>Tre là một loại tài nguyên có thể tái tạo, có thể thu thập được bằng cách chặt hạ Bamboo Patch bằng Dao Rựa trong Shipwrecked DLC. Nó cũng có thể thu được bằng cách đập Nhà Lợn Roan hoặc Đầu Lợn Roan.</p>",
  "title": "Bamboo",
  "wikitext": "{{Exclusivity|Shipwrecked|Hamlet}}\n{{Object Infobox\n|icon = Bamboo.png\n|image = Bamboo Dropped.png\n|burnTime = [[File:Light_Sources_Filter.png|32px|link=Fuel#Fire Fuel]] 45 sec\n|stack = 40\n|droppedBy = {{Pic|24|Bamboo Patch}} ({{Pic|24|Machete}}{{Pic|24|Shears}}) {{Pic|32|Blue Whale Carcass}} {{Pic|32|White Whale Carcass}} {{Pic|20|Slotmachine}}\n|soldBy = {{Pic|32|'The Sty' Oddities Emporium}} ({{Pic|24|Oinc}} &times;3) {{Pic|24|Hamlet icon}}\n|spawnCode = \"bamboo\"}}\n{{Quotes\n|wolfgang=Very mighty building material!\n|wilson=Maybe I can bamboozle my enemies with this?\n|willow=Looks flammable.\n|woodie=It's like diet wood, eh?\n|maxwell=I have several ideas in mind for this.\n|wagstaff=A versatile and pliable perennial plant I can use to make stuff.\n|wendy=Green sticks... who cares...\n|woodlegs=Ye'd be too big ta pick me teeth wit'. If me had teeth...\n|wickerbottom=A useful material of high tensile strength.\n|webber=Such a useful stick-type thing.\n|warly=Bamboo shoots are excellent on a nice bed of rice.\n|wx78=IT'S A VERSATILE ENGINEERING MATERIAL\n|walani=This looks pretty float-atious.\n|wigfrid=Sticks öf great versatility.\n|wilba=IS'T TREE STUFFS O' BENDINESS\n|wormwood=Greenstick\n|wheeler=One piece is nice. Many pieces are nicer.\n|choose=wilson}}\n'''Bamboo''' is a [[Renewable resources|renewable]] resource that can be gathered by hacking down a [[Bamboo Patch]] with a [[Machete]] in the ''[[Don't Starve: Shipwrecked|Shipwrecked]]'' DLC. It can also be obtained by hammering a [[Wildbore House]] or a [[Wildbore Head]].\n\nIt is used in many [[Nautical]] recipes and can also be refined into [[Cloth]].\n\n=={{Pic|32|Hamlet icon}} Hamlet==\nBamboo is also included in the ''[[Don't Starve: Hamlet|Hamlet]]'' DLC where it can be bought for 3 [[Oinc]]s at [['The Sty' Oddities Emporium]] in the [[Pig City]]. There is also a small chance(around 7%) for Bamboo to be obtained from hammering the [[A Smashing Pot|'A Smashing Pot]]. Using a [[Shears]] on a Bamboo Patch will result in 2 [[Bamboo]] instead of the usual one. \n\n=={{Pic|32|Icon Tools}} Usage==\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Bamboo\n|count1 = 3\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Cloth}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Bamboo\n|count1 = 4\n|item2 = Vine\n|count2 = 3\n|result = Raft}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Bamboo\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Vine\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Palm Leaf\n|count3 = 4\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Thatch Sail}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Bamboo\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Cloth\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Rope\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Cloth Sail}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Bamboo\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Rope\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Doydoy Feather\n|count3 = 4\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Feather Lite Sail}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Bamboo\n|count1 = 4\n|item2 = Rope\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Quacken Beak\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Quackering Ram}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Bamboo\n|count1 = 4\n|item2 = Limestone\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Coconut\n|count3 = 2\n|result = Tar Extractor}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Bamboo\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Rope\n|count2 = 3\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Trawl Net}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Bamboo\n|count1 = 2\n|item2 = Vine\n|item3 = Seaweed\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Mussel Stick}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Bamboo\n|count1 = 3\n|item2 = Jellyfish\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Spear Gun}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Bamboo\n|count1 = 4\n|item2 = Palm Leaf\n|count2 = 4\n|item3 = Rope\n|count3 = 3\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Palm Leaf Hut}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Bamboo\n|count1 = 8\n|item2 = Palm Leaf\n|count2 = 5\n|item3 = Pig Skin\n|count3 = 4\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Wildbore House}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Bamboo\n|count1 = 5\n|item2 = Electrical Doodad\n|count2 = 2\n|item3 = Thermal Stone\n|tool = Alchemy Engine\n|result = Ice Maker 3000}}\n{{Recipe\n|item1 = Bamboo\n|count1 = 4\n|item2 = Empty Bottle\n|item3 = Bioluminescence\n|count3 = 2\n|tool = Science Machine\n|result = Buoy}}\n=={{Pic|32|Placeholder}} Trivia==\n* It was originally assumed that Bamboo was a Wood Food Type and could also be eaten by Werebeaver and would give 10 Beaverness\n{{Resources}}\n\n[[de:Bambus]]\n[[es:Bambú]]\n[[pl:Bambus (DSS)]]\n[[vi:Tre]]\n[[Category:Resources]]\n[[Category:Fuel]]\n[[Category:Flammable Objects]]\n[[Category:Mob Dropped Items]]"
